                        <li>Topic will sort the Reviews by Topic alphabetically</li>
                    </ul>
                    <img src="~/Content/Howto/Sort.png"/>
                </p>
                <p>You can combine the search and sort functions by first searching and then sorting the results. If you sort a list of results, and then enter a new search, the sort will return to default</p>
